{"id":"271553937_SoDA_Dynamic_visual_analytics_of_big_social_data","abstract":"In this work we apply dynamic visual analytics on big social data by the example of microblogs from Twitter. Thereby, we address current challenges like real-time analytics as well as analyses of unstructured data. To this end, we propose SoDA - a concept enabling the integrated analysis of the dimensions: message, location and time. Furthermore, we introduce a novel design for tag cloud visualizations, the weighted tag network, offering enhanced semantic insights. All concepts are fully implemented and evaluated by a comprehensive software prototype in different application scenarios.","authors":["Sabri Hassan","Johannes Saenger","GÃ¼nther Pernul"],"meta":["January 2014","DOI:10.1109/BIGCOMP.2014.6741433","Conference: 2014 International Conference on Big Data and Smart Computing (BIGCOMP)"],"references":["277007765_Mastering_The_Information_Age_-_Solving_Problems_with_Visual_Analytics","258143454_Incremental_Visual_Text_Analytics_of_News_Story_Development","257719316_Solving_Problems_with_Visual_Analytics","254995412_Top_Ten_Interaction_Challenges_in_Extreme-Scale_Visual_Analytics","240918109_Is_the_Sample_Good_Enough_Comparing_Data_from_Twitter's_Streaming_API_with_Twitter's_Firehose","236962802_Visualization_of_social_media_Seeing_a_mirage_or_a_message","221517807_TwitInfo_Aggregating_and_Visualizing_Microblogs_for_Event_Exploration","308376248_Interactive_dynamics_for_visual_analysis","304929258_3-D_Data_Management_Controlling_Data_Volume_Velocity_and_Variety","304535150_Big_data_The_management_revolution","261861945_Interactive_Dynamics_for_Visual_Analysis","261483230_LeadLine_Interactive_visual_analysis_of_text_data_through_event_identification_and_exploration","260584436_Big_Data's_Big_Unintended_Consequences","260584072_Real-Time_Visual_Analytics_for_Text_Streams","257416894_Dynamic_Visual_Analytics_-_Facing_the_Real-Time_Challenge","232656799_On_the_Beauty_and_Usability_of_Tag_Cl